<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Update Your 433a Information</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #2a7ae2;">Hi {{name}},</h2>
          <p>We’re actively discussing your case with the tax authorities, and
            we’re ready to take the next step toward resolution. To do that, we
            need to make sure your financial information is still accurate.</p>
          <p>They consider the collection information statement a time-sensitive
            document. If anything has changed—your income, expenses, job, or
            household—we’ll need to update it together. An outdated form could
            lead to results that don’t reflect your situation, or delay your
            progress entirely.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">We’re ready to go over
            it with you, one-on-one, over the phone.</p>
          <p>Call us at
            <a
              href="tel:{{number}}"
              style="color: #2a7ae2; text-decoration: none;"
            >{{number}}</a>
            so we can keep your case moving forward.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>